### 

Async => Not occuring at the same time

when it is used

1. Fetch data from server
2. Want to execute something with a delay
3. Want to execute something after an event 


majority of asynchronous javascript is triggered by 

1.Browser APIs /Web APIs
2. Event based handlers e.g setTimeout, click, mouseover etc
3. Promises

